item.title: CVE-2023-0749|2023-03-13T16:03:31.466Z -- unknown -- ocean%20extra
item.description: The Ocean Extra WordPress plugin before 2.1.3 does not ensure that the template to be loaded via a shortcode is actually a template, allowing any authenticated users such as subscriber to retrieve the content of arbitrary posts, such as draft, private or even password protected ones.
